title: 7.18 Deploy - Thursday 14th Sept @ 05.00am AEST
body:
Hi Folks

Due to some last minute bugfixes to the 7.18 patch, our regular Wednesday morning window has been pushed back by 1 day for this patch only.

Patch 7.18 should be going out to the OCE servers tomorrow morning (Thursday 14th Sept).   While you wait, why not check out the [patch notes](http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/patch/patch-718-notes)

Cheers
Mindstar
